{"tid":1975444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重開】就花你五分鐘時間，入嚟登記做選民?","createTime":"2020-04-16T14:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T00:52:30.000Z","uid":37971,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"973aef44fef84cd5d66b2e98b58b4c3b4a38589e","tid":1975444,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:05:58.000Z","msg":"登一登記都係五分鐘啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EaKJzbW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEaKJzbW.jpg&h=faca3aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nlink都畀埋你喇 <a href=\"https://hk2020.vote/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote%2F&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10AfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=4fe54fe1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote/</a><br />\n未登記嘅，依家就花五分鐘登一登記啦，好嗎?<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重點：<br />\n登記咗嘅，都唔好上一頁住！幫手手動轉埋張圖出去啦，好嗎?</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好再話投票無用，選舉無用<br />\n你連投票權都唔要嘅話，咁你就連影響個制度嘅能力都無<br />\n到頭嚟，你就只能夠做一個旁觀者，睇住個結果畀人操控<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後就要靠大家幫手推了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b2fbc5c08b4bd48f55806c5f3fed8578720ced","tid":1975444,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:06:43.000Z","msg":"一個人推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03bf68f2b1ab8cc2fcf2b52192651c0c393ac92e","tid":1975444,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:07:35.000Z","msg":"幫幫手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77c7dba93c9dbeff990325eab4b61c6dd7eceaf","tid":1975444,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:08:33.000Z","msg":"無人幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7092b0eebd6dab4e89610e354ae6bcc9fc1efbab","tid":1975444,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT